{"lemma":"تَفِل","slug":"تَفِل","root":"ت.ف.ل","root_slug":"ت-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ت-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n3969","n3971","n3972","n3973","n3974","n3975"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3969","headword_ar":"تَفَلَ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafila","text_ar":"تَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafolN","text_ar":"تَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaqa","text_ar":"بَصَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [or rather,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he spat, emitting a small quantity of saliva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in scattered portions, as when one spits forth some minute thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~afolu","text_ar":"التَّفْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albazoqu","text_ar":"البَزْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but less in degree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb: *) the first degree is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albazoqu","text_ar":"البَزْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~afolu","text_ar":"التَّفْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~afovu","text_ar":"النَّفْثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~afoxu","text_ar":"النَّفْخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~afolu","text_ar":"التَّفْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"with the mouth is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"never without somewhat of spittle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a blowing without spittle is [said to be] termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafovN","text_ar":"نَفْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafolu Alr~aAqiY","text_ar":"تَفْلُ الرَّاقِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The spitting of the charmer, in which he emits a small quantity of saliva at a time, in scattered portions:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafava","text_ar":"نَفَثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAqa maA='a AlbaHori fatafalahu","text_ar":"ذَاقَ مَا=ءَ البَحْرِ فَتَفَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tasted the water of the sea, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spirted it forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of dislike thereof. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafila","text_ar":"تَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafalN","text_ar":"تَفَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became altered for the worse in odour, ill-smelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frouzy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was unperfumed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume, and so became altered for the worse in odour, ill-smelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frouzy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafilato","text_ar":"تَفِلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stank, by reason of having neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume and ointments:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she perfumed herself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus bearing two contr. significations. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","T","Mgh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n3971","headword_ar":"تَفْلٌ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3972","headword_ar":"تُفْلٌ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafolN","text_ar":"تَفْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, accord. to the TT,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tufaAlN","text_ar":"تُفَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) vulgarly ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tifolN","text_ar":"تِفْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tifaAlN","text_ar":"تِفَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spittle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saliva, ejected from the mouth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buSaAqN","text_ar":"بُصَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafalN","text_ar":"تَفَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ibn-Abi-l- Hadeed, TA:) or it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buSaAq","text_ar":"بُصَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See 1.] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Froth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foam,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) of the sea; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":309}],"source_refs":["K","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n3973","headword_ar":"تِفْلٌ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tufolN","text_ar":"تُفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aSaAba fulaAnN mino fulaAnK A_il~aA","text_ar":"مَا اَصَابَ فُلَانٌ مِنْ فُلَانٍ اـِلَّا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tifolFA TafiyfFA","text_ar":"تِفْلًا طَفِيفًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one obtained not from such a one save a little."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3974","headword_ar":"تَفَلٌ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tufolN","text_ar":"تُفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3975","headword_ar":"تَفِلٌ","root":"tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a man; (S, M, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafilapN","text_ar":"تَفِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a woman, (T, M, Mgh, Msb, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mitofaAlN","text_ar":"مِتْفَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb, K,) which is a possessive epithet, (M,) or an intensive epithet, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Altered for the worse in odour, ill-smelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frouzy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unperfumed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume, and so become altered for the worse in odour, illsmelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frouzy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stinking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of having neglected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left off the use of, perfume and ointments:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafilapN","text_ar":"تَفِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafilaAtN","text_ar":"تَفِلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, Mgh, Msb;) applied to such women as are not to be prevented from going to the mosque, and in this case meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unperfumed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * Mgh, * TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN safilapN tafilapN","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ سَفِلَةٌ تَفِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company of men of the lowest and vilest sort"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","M","Mgh","Msb","K","S","TA"]}]}}